										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p data-track="2">正所谓“人间烟火气，最抚凡人心”，柴米油盐酱醋茶，一日三餐应四季，承载着烟火气的美食是最能抚慰人心的，大家好，我是晓峰。“六月芳菲满人间，花红柳绿香满园”，夏天是美好的，有小桥流水催生的浪漫柔情；有草原牛马奔腾的生生不息；有金色沙漠和红色山岩的热情似火；也有皑皑雪山和深邃峡谷的圣洁清凉，更有着数不尽的应季水果，叫你一饱口腹之欲。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-395" title="24550b3da3d54e5b8af1f1c0d57ce656" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/24550b3da3d54e5b8af1f1c0d57ce656.jpg" alt="24550b3da3d54e5b8af1f1c0d57ce656" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/24550b3da3d54e5b8af1f1c0d57ce656.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/24550b3da3d54e5b8af1f1c0d57ce656-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/24550b3da3d54e5b8af1f1c0d57ce656-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="4">韩国作家金爱烂的短篇小说集《你的夏天还好吗》中记载：“身体总是率先察觉，站出来要求一些东西：比如农历新年想吃年糕汤，十五想吃野菜，中秋想吃松糕，生日想喝海带汤，冬至想喝红豆粥……只有这样，胃肠感觉舒服，身体才会接受新的季节”，细细品味，的确是这么回事，夏季来临，我已经迫不及待地想大口吃西瓜了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-396" title="3ed181ad7f284810a1660e31e75a034c" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3ed181ad7f284810a1660e31e75a034c.jpg" alt="3ed181ad7f284810a1660e31e75a034c" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3ed181ad7f284810a1660e31e75a034c.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3ed181ad7f284810a1660e31e75a034c-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/3ed181ad7f284810a1660e31e75a034c-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="6">西瓜是夏天独有的盛宴，它清凉解渴，味道甘甜，其含水量高达95%，能很好地补充由于出汗而消耗的水分；它还富含大量的葡萄糖、蔗糖、苹果酸、果糖、蛋白氨基酸以及丰富的维生素C等物质，是一种集营养和口味极佳的水果，因此西瓜也成为了夏季的解暑神器，炎炎夏日来上一块凉爽香甜的冰镇西瓜，真的是透心凉~心飞扬！</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-397" title="1fd80406450d4537b9a7b7be48ee9dcd" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1fd80406450d4537b9a7b7be48ee9dcd.jpg" alt="1fd80406450d4537b9a7b7be48ee9dcd" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1fd80406450d4537b9a7b7be48ee9dcd.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1fd80406450d4537b9a7b7be48ee9dcd-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/1fd80406450d4537b9a7b7be48ee9dcd-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="14">通常情况下，我们吃西瓜时，都会将西瓜皮当垃圾一样扔掉，其实“瓜皮”也是宝贝，它的营养价值和西瓜瓤一样，富含蛋白质、脂肪、碳水化合物、膳食纤维和人体所必需的微量元素，而且口感又不同于西瓜瓤，用来炒尖椒或是做成西瓜糖都很美味。我家每次吃剩的西瓜皮我都不舍得扔，腌一腌再放到锅里炒一炒，清凉又去火，味道美极了，不懂吃真可惜！下面我就分享一下具体做法：</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-398" title="b2672b780cb3479d93f4e0c78b75846e" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b2672b780cb3479d93f4e0c78b75846e.jpg" alt="b2672b780cb3479d93f4e0c78b75846e" width="900" height="740" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b2672b780cb3479d93f4e0c78b75846e.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b2672b780cb3479d93f4e0c78b75846e-300x247.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/b2672b780cb3479d93f4e0c78b75846e-768x631.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="15">1、吃剩下的西瓜皮先将最外层绿色的、口感很硬的外皮削掉不要，冲洗干净后，切成6毫米左右厚的西瓜条备用；注意一点，做西瓜糖用的瓜皮不要吃得太干净了，我觉得留下1公分左右的红色瓜瓤，做出来的西瓜糖会更加漂亮好看。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-399" title="780e135c41d541a2963a7f08a3427862" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/780e135c41d541a2963a7f08a3427862.jpg" alt="780e135c41d541a2963a7f08a3427862" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/780e135c41d541a2963a7f08a3427862.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/780e135c41d541a2963a7f08a3427862-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/780e135c41d541a2963a7f08a3427862-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="16">2、切好的西瓜条放入大盆中，然后加入两把白糖并且抓拌均匀，再盖上保鲜膜，放到冰箱里冷藏腌制备用。一般腌制一个晚上就可以了，这一步的目的是腌制出西瓜皮里面的水分，另外，也是为了增加香甜的口感。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-400" title="7fa87964db504176a90c3a8ae03dc379" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7fa87964db504176a90c3a8ae03dc379.jpg" alt="7fa87964db504176a90c3a8ae03dc379" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7fa87964db504176a90c3a8ae03dc379.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7fa87964db504176a90c3a8ae03dc379-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/7fa87964db504176a90c3a8ae03dc379-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="17">3、西瓜条腌制一晚上后取出和腌出来的汁水一起倒入锅中，不要再另外加水，开大火开始熬制，大约熬制十几分钟左右，可以看到西瓜水快熬干了，这时我们转成中火，然后用铲子不停地翻炒，防止西瓜皮粘到锅底、糊锅。这一步时间会有点久，要有耐心，炒至西瓜皮黏黏的、晶莹透亮时即可关火，盛出晾凉后就可以开吃了。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-401" title="ddbf7dab63ac4928aac540ee8efd2550" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ddbf7dab63ac4928aac540ee8efd2550.jpg" alt="ddbf7dab63ac4928aac540ee8efd2550" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ddbf7dab63ac4928aac540ee8efd2550.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ddbf7dab63ac4928aac540ee8efd2550-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ddbf7dab63ac4928aac540ee8efd2550-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-402" title="ac47916c954d472b9198d8f9d2dc812f" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ac47916c954d472b9198d8f9d2dc812f.jpg" alt="ac47916c954d472b9198d8f9d2dc812f" width="900" height="609" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ac47916c954d472b9198d8f9d2dc812f.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ac47916c954d472b9198d8f9d2dc812f-300x203.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/ac47916c954d472b9198d8f9d2dc812f-768x520.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-403" title="237ee94ee8564f15a2dced7f277bc417" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/237ee94ee8564f15a2dced7f277bc417.jpg" alt="237ee94ee8564f15a2dced7f277bc417" width="900" height="695" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/237ee94ee8564f15a2dced7f277bc417.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/237ee94ee8564f15a2dced7f277bc417-300x232.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/237ee94ee8564f15a2dced7f277bc417-768x593.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
<p class="pgc-img-caption">
</div>
<p data-track="19">这水果全身都是宝，很多人只吃果肉，其实“果皮”也是宝贝，简单一炒清凉爽口，好吃不上火。这样做的西瓜皮很有嚼劲，可以直接当糖吃，也可以夹到馒头或面包里当果酱吃，还可以用来泡水喝，清新爽口又开胃。吃不完的装到玻璃瓶子里密封好，再放到冰箱里冷藏保存，随吃随取特别方便，能吃十几天都不坏。</p>
<div class="pgc-img"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-404" title="cf1cf09665a34f75ba4603942914c78b" src="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/cf1cf09665a34f75ba4603942914c78b.jpg" alt="cf1cf09665a34f75ba4603942914c78b" width="900" height="506" srcset="https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/cf1cf09665a34f75ba4603942914c78b.jpg 900w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/cf1cf09665a34f75ba4603942914c78b-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.huacao77.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/cf1cf09665a34f75ba4603942914c78b-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></div>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
